OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1782134325
OL,3,C'I didn't want to risk it': Hodgkinson
OL,4,C'healthy' after UK Championships exit
OL,6,FBut a visibly emotional Hodgkinson
OL,7,Fsparked concern when she abruptly
OL,8,Fpulled out but Jenny Meadows, who
OL,9,Falongside husband Trevor Painter
OL,10,Fcoaches Hodgkinson, later confirmed a
OL,11,Fphysiotherapist gave her "the all-
OL,12,Fclear".
OL,14,FSpeaking immediately after dropping
OL,15,Fout of the final, Hodgkinson said: "I
OL,16,Fwasn't feeling 100% standing on the
OL,17,Fstart line, so I made the tough
OL,18,Fdecision to step away and not race. I
OL,19,Fdidn't want to risk anything this
OL,20,Fsummer."
OL,26,@sD@ZOUtD@FO]wD@dOU|D@HO]
