OL,3,C'I didn't want to risk it': Hodgkinson
OL,4,C'healthy' after UK Championships exit
OL,6,FThe world indoor 800m record-holder
OL,7,Flater wrote on Instagram: "Leaving
OL,8,Fchamps healthy! Sometimes the hard
OL,9,Fdecision is saying no. Body wasn't
OL,10,Ffeeling 100%, exciting summer ahead!"
OL,12,FMeadows replied to a concerned fan on
OL,13,FX, saying "Thankfully it was just a
OL,14,Fprecautionary measure. She's fine now
OL,15,Fshe's seen the physio and got the all
OL,16,Fclear."
OL,26,@oD@[OUrD@eO]uD@KOUxD@GO]
