PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1782134325
OL,3,C'I didn't want to risk it': Hodgkinson
OL,4,C'healthy' after UK Championships exit
OL,6,FShe further explained to another user:
OL,7,F"She's not injured! It was a
OL,8,Fprecaution as her hamstring felt
OL,9,Ftight. She did her cool down jog, saw
OL,10,Fthe physio and is fine. We don't take
OL,11,Fany risks now and neither does Keely."
OL,13,FHodgkinson's training partner Georgia
OL,14,FHunter Bell won the women's 800m final
OL,15,Fin a championship-record one minute,
OL,16,F55.93 seconds.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@fO]
